                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.001M26.</note>
                        <head>[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico
                                        City</hi></placeName>. <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-11-06"><hi rend="italic">November 6,
                                1911</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>On this date President Madero was inaugurated.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson.</hi></signed></closer>
